3. Roland firmware (SC-55 / SC-55mk2 / CM-300 / JV-880 / etc. ROMs)
-------------------------------------------------------------------

   The Nuked-SC55 emulator requires ROM image files originating from
   Roland hardware. Those ROMs are copyrighted by Roland Corporation
   and are NOT distributed with this project. You must supply your own
   ROM dumps, which you should obtain only by legal means (typically
   by dumping the chips from hardware you own).

   The application loads ROMs at runtime from a directory you specify.
   No ROM content is bundled in any way.


